FBIS4-29276 "dreas116_d_94022" FBIS-EAS-94-116 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 South Korea Defense Ministry Plans To Give Daily Briefing Defense Ministry Plans To Give Daily Briefing SK1606023894 Seoul YONHAP in English 0231 GMT 16 Jun 94 SK1606023894 Seoul YONHAP English BFN [Text] Seoul, June 16 (YONHAP) -- The Defense Ministry said Thursday it will hold a daily press briefing to keep ordinary citizens abreast of the military situation and help dispel public anxiety. The daily press briefings will continue until the current crisis is resolved, officials said.
